   Hiring Employees
   When hiring employees, you must verify their employment eligibility,
   name, and social security number, and have them fill out a Form W-4.

   Refer to the Small Business Administration's Employees: How of Find and
   Pay Them (PDF).

   Recordkeeping for Employers
   Keep all records of employment taxes for at least four years.


